{"tid":1115150,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日搭香港航空去大阪，驚佢汁，買唔買旅遊保？","createTime":"2019-04-19T03:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T17:07:47.000Z","uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5890a009c689b9583f5c9c4afeb031ff3dbc05b3","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">機票酒店公司搞 公司俾錢<br />\n公司買左人壽保only<br />\n<br />\n但我地成班同事<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一早上Kloxxx買晒套票同埋車票</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n睇蘋果報導，又再上fb睇下, 講到佢地好有問題，而家好擔心佢地會close呀。<br />\n<br />\n怎麼辦好？<br />\n<br />\n剛睇左藍十字既航空公司倒閉，已經講明香港航空唔會包！？即係點？</span>"},{"pid":"a5e5fa145b4d139d4057f5e92a635349a36a0495","tid":1115150,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a7c19d6bc25d1b983c3607423401798fca21d4","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"仲有如果我地公司同事一行13人買旅遊保 包航空公司倒閉 有賠償<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有冇邊間有推介？13個人一齊買有冇discount?</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7f2bffcbcacd7c4b64717cf2e93901963b2e0ae0","tid":1115150,"uid":132462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1896b2f755dcbd45bb5c0b820826a6a491ba5c62","tid":1115150,"uid":23087,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"大阪地下鐵，成人用小童飛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1098580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1098580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n食屎啦 樓主"},{"pid":"1ce5ad1dbd236e58aaaa3812a7b7223ebcd34d21","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"1896b2f755dcbd45bb5c0b820826a6a491ba5c62","tid":1115150,"uid":23087,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"大阪地下鐵，成人用小童飛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1098580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1098580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n食屎啦 樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"下 同事幫晒成組人買晒周遊卷了"},{"pid":"a873a790e210b061b196541fa6e6a5aae9e63bad","tid":1115150,"uid":30098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1896b2f755dcbd45bb5c0b820826a6a491ba5c62","tid":1115150,"uid":23087,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"大阪地下鐵，成人用小童飛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1098580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1098580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n食屎啦 樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27e830c6b8b8d564782cb7c859e62d63e292742a","tid":1115150,"uid":248703,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7a6939ec729760fa07f9bde64fd3ff7a6a63d89","tid":1115150,"uid":248703,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68af3a036d3a2a5542af7ac6e13085e60ea1331c","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"當中經理帶埋佢老公黎 <br />\n佢地買左旅遊保 但睇左條款唔包航空公司倒閉<br />\n<br />\n如果假返航班delay or 行李唔見左<br />\n而佢又買左2份旅遊保<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以claim2間公司？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家好擔心香港航空會出事呀。<br />\nD新聞報導講到好恐怖<br />\n我仲有一日就出發<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家可否幫幫手一齊集氣<br />\n保佑香港航空過埋24號 等我返左香港先再搞呀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好驚</span>"},{"pid":"33fb3162b362ccf6d061a2a1a45ff155e32876cd","tid":1115150,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"汁你老母"},{"pid":"817882ce2d96c8c7152dd98d957923f781c7ded8","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190418/59503086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F59503086&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=9c68405c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F59503086&h=53c80c42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190418/59503086</a><br />\n<br />\n睇蘋果動 hk01....<br />\n佢地尋日仲提早關門 好恐怖<br />\n我好驚佢地倒閉<br />\n會搞到我去唔到旅行<br />\n我地成班同事買晒kloxxx既車票 一日團<br />\n而家先黎玩野？不了.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">請大家一齊集氣保佑佢地24前都順利營運...<br />\n我地24號先從大阪回港...</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n邊間旅遊保險包航空公司倒閉？而家買仲趕唔趕得到？"},{"pid":"6bdf89c01328114b22bc70ef4308bdad50838327","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"早唔搞 遲唔搞<br />\n係要撞正公司一年一度既公司旅行先搞d咁既野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唉 <br />\n希望香港航空平安渡過呢個難關<br />\n班股東唔好搞事<br />\n唔好把小市民既利益放係佢地角力權力上<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"160f7874a2bee1f8f40f35c428ae1ff6d28bb9bc","tid":1115150,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bf90c7042933a9e1444130cfc7c208d08ebc54e","tid":1115150,"uid":56720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ec0618a8e8bef40ea11f141c23934c79c350b52","tid":1115150,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"160f7874a2bee1f8f40f35c428ae1ff6d28bb9bc","tid":1115150,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"多謝你回覆先<br />\n睇到藍十字都講明唔包香港航空倒閉既任何保險陪償<br />\n我更加擔心<br />\n<br />\n最慘係<br />\n我老細叫我去搵 好多同事都係年紀大唔識呢d野<br />\n<br />\n我睇左幾間都冇講呢d萬一倒閉既細項陪償<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最慘係如果買要唔要輸入佢地個人資料？<br />\n我只係個英文全名, 部門名，職位同佢地員工號碼。<br />\n<br />\n更多既資料我又冇 生日日期問左hr又冇覆<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做1/3個活動搞手都係伏"},{"pid":"39036247bfeff6a5d54048fd241721c240f692e1","tid":1115150,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0d0a0874976ecd21f80418cba8b79371dc5b4b5","tid":1115150,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27d736eb7f84b51368196063098108ebcb7faaef","tid":1115150,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33fb3162b362ccf6d061a2a1a45ff155e32876cd","tid":1115150,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"汁你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>汁你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b7bd5c0b6d4143e2a38a92fc9dc9c97eb78daabb","tid":1115150,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗買啦，到時佢執笠你就係債權人，你攞埋佢部機飛曬全日本都得。"},{"pid":"fc71b818f497bde50cdda789c8daf2e59d452c90","tid":1115150,"uid":235671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1896b2f755dcbd45bb5c0b820826a6a491ba5c62","tid":1115150,"uid":23087,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"大阪地下鐵，成人用小童飛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1098580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1098580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n食屎啦 樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"條友問叫雞同小童飛....呢D唔死都無用。有錢叫雞無錢買成人飛"},{"pid":"eeeca54317cb043b3365e076335d65a0ee1854a2","tid":1115150,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1171c1